data.title: SIERRA 4-Position Ignition Switch Conventional, Accessory-Off-Run-Start
data.meta_description: Shop SIERRA 4-Position Ignition Switch Conventional, Accessory-Off-Run-Start at West Marine. Visit for prices, reviews, deals and more!
data.text:
Exact OEM replacement ignition switch for Seadog part number 420375-1.

Sierra's Polyester Ignition Switch fits a standard 7/8"dia. hole and features a four-position conventional switch that provides Accessory-Off-Run-Start. Includes two keys and different key codes for added security.

Key Features

Maximum corrosion protection eliminates oxidation

Inner seal between cylinder lock and contact plate

Non-conductive housing eliminates potential shorts

Four-position conventional switch

Exact OEM replacement for Seadog 420375-1

Specifications

Material: Marine-grade glass-filled polyester

Length: Long, 1 1/8" maximum panel thickness

Hole Size: 7/8"

Terminal Type: 4 screw tab

Back Up Nut: Brass

Face Nut: Knurled black plastic with snap-on rubber cap

Positions: Accessory-Off-Run-Start

Rated

Ignition: 15A @ 12V DC

Solenoid: 30A @ 12V DC

Accessory: 15A @ 12V DC

The Sierra Engine Parts Selector
